Interface Summary
JackBufferSizeCallback Implement this interface and set on client to be informed if the buffersize changes.
JackClientRegistrationCallback A JACK client registration callback which is called when a JACK client is registered or unregistered.
JackGraphOrderCallback Called when the JACK graph order is changed.
JackPortConnectCallback A JACK callback which is invoked when two ports and connected or disconnected.
JackPortRegistrationCallback A JACK Port registration callback which is invoked when a Port is registered or unregistered.
JackProcessCallback Implement this interface and set on client to be called on every process cycle.
JackSampleRateCallback Implement this interface and set on client to be informed if the sample rate changes.
